{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'All the weird stuff I said before... Just pretend that never happened.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'I wanted to answer you.', 3: '6', 4: 'That might be a bit hard.', 5: '6'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "There are many things I don't like about this squad, but what I don't like most is you...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Well, that came out of the blue.', 3: '8', 4: "I didn't say anything to make you mad, did I?", 5: '9'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Well, I always speak my mind.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'You make me so mad!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "You're just an ordinary commandant, but you always do the impossible.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'You always have the silliest tactics, but they always work out as expected.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "You don't have our combat ability, yet you're stronger than all of us...", 4: '1'}
{2: "Sounds like that's a compliment.", 3: '14', 4: 'Sorry...?', 5: '14'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'And you have such a contagious attitude!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "That's why I don't like you. Put simply, I can't stand anything about you.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I can't stand your undying optimism!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I can't stand that you treat everyone fairly!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I can't stand that... you always bond with other Constructs!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Am I not strong enough? Or do you think I'm...", 4: '1'}
